      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、少し撮影が押しちゃって",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、仕事ですから仕方ありません\n次の現場にはまだ間に合いますから",
      "startTime": 7.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1019502163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわ。次はトークショーの仕事よね\n確か、人気のコスメを展示するイベントだったかしら",
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 17.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 18.1111327013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　マズいな。予約したタクシーが渋滞に捕まって\n来られないみたいです。新しいのを探さないと……",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8552.3602984,
          "startTime": 31.4856936317
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら電車を乗り継いで行きましょう\nほら、急ぎなさい、走るわよ！",
      "startTime": 29.9666678111,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
