      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9103640081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "トークショー、無事終えることが出来て良かったわね\n遅刻もしないで済んだし",
      "startTime": 44.0000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、スケジュールが分刻みで……\nBIG4になってから仕事が殺到してしまって",
      "startTime": 49.8333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.721749449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
